<Link id="l00294" /><CodeLine lineNumber="294"><Highlight kind="comment">  /// interior node of the inheritance tree, to make it easier to read the</Highlight></CodeLine>

<Link id="l00296" /><CodeLine lineNumber="296"><Highlight kind="comment">  ///</Highlight></CodeLine>
